CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.5
-----------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o Add new functions ('xMLdotplot', 'xMLdensity', 'xMLzoom') for visualising machine learning results

    o Add a new function ('xGSsimulator') for simulating gold standard negatives
    
    o Add new functions ('xPierGSEA', 'xGSEAdotplot', 'xGSEAbarplot') for gene set enrichment analysis of prioritisation results
    

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.3
-----------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o Initialise integral functions ('xMLrandomforest') for machine learning
    
    o Allow parallel computing on Windows
    
    o Speed up the calculation of defining and scoring seed genes from SNP or genomic regions
    
    
CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.1
-----------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o Add new functions ('xPredictROCR', 'xPredictCompare', 'xContour') for performance evaluation
    
    o Add new functions ('xSNPhic.r', 'xPCHiCplot.r') for dealing with promoter capture HiC data

    o Modify the function 'xPierSNPs.r' to incorporate promoter capture HiC data
    
    
CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
-----------------------

NEW FEATURES

    o A genomic-led target prioritisation system

    o Leveraging genetic data to prioritise targets at the gene, pathway and network level
